1. Treatment satisfaction was high among the subjects.
2. The majority of subjects stated they would repeat the treatment.
3. The majority of subjects stated they would recommend the treatment to friends.
4. At each time point, a higher proportion of subjects was more satisfied with the CPM-26-treated side of the face.
